               10  w-tin-ele-wci.
                   15  w-tin-ele-wci-des  pic  x(50)                  .
                   15  w-tin-ele-wci-ast  pic  x(01)                  .
                   15  w-tin-ele-wci-alf  pic  x(10)                  .
